summary: so, the whole time im watching any movie with thanos in it i just feel... uncomfortable. like, theres a feeling of familiarity...
body:
why endgame made me so uncomfortable

so, the whole time im watching any movie with thanos in it i just feel… uncomfortable. like, theres a feeling of familiarity that made everything that takes place just feel wrong. and im thinking why, trying to find out why im feeling so off about this character and then i realize

thanos looks like my dad

my dad takes like two pictures a year but let me sum it up for you: my dads almost always bald, has a very rectangle face, the same eye shape and eyebrow structure, and fuck, look at the nose.

in conclusion my brain thought thanos was my dad
